official_title: Feasibility of a Pilot Intervention Designed to Increase SNAP Fruit and Vegetable Incentive Program Use for Families With Food Insecurity
inclusion_criteria:
* 18 years of age or older
* Had a child 2-17 years of age
* Child lived in their home 50% of the time or more
* Child was a patient of the general pediatrics clinic enrolled in this study
* English-speaking
* Enrolled in SNAP
* Experiencing household food insecurity

Caregiver
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
exclusion_criteria: * Had purchased fruits and vegetables within the past year at the community food site participating in this study
